037/**
038 * Event handler implementation for the {@link GoslinParser}.
039 *
040 * @author Dominik Kopczynski
041 * @author Nils Hoffmann
042 */
043public class GoslinParserEventHandler extends LipidBaseParserEventHandler {
044
045    private int dbPosition;
046    private String dbCistrans;
047    private char plasmalogen;
048    private String mediatorFunction;
049    private final ArrayList<Integer> mediatorFunctionPositions = new ArrayList<>();
050    private boolean mediatorSuffix;
051
052    private final static Map<String, Integer> MEDIATOR_FA = Map.of(
053            "H", 17, "O", 18, "E", 20, "Do", 22);
054    private final static Map<String, Integer> MEDIATOR_DB = Map.of(
055            "M", 1, "D", 2, "Tr", 3, "T", 4, "P", 5, "H", 6);

057    /**
058     * Create a new {@code GoslinParserEventHandler}.
059     *
060     * @param knownFunctionalGroups the known functional groups
061     */
062    public GoslinParserEventHandler(KnownFunctionalGroups knownFunctionalGroups) {
063        super(knownFunctionalGroups);
064        try {
065            registeredEvents = Map.ofEntries(
066                    entry("lipid_pre_event", this::resetParser),
067                    entry("lipid_post_event", this::buildLipid),
068                    entry("hg_cl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
069                    entry("hg_mlcl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
070                    entry("hg_pl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
071                    entry("hg_lpl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
072                    entry("hg_lsl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
073                    entry("hg_so_lsl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
074                    entry("hg_dsl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
075                    entry("st_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
076                    entry("hg_ste_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
077                    entry("hg_stes_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
078                    entry("hg_mgl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
079                    entry("hg_dgl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
080                    entry("hg_sgl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
081                    entry("hg_tgl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
082                    entry("hg_dlcl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
083                    entry("hg_sac_di_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
084                    entry("hg_sac_f_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
085                    entry("hg_tpl_pre_event", this::setHeadGroupName),
086                    entry("gl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
087                    entry("pl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
088                    entry("sl_species_pre_event", this::setSpeciesLevel),
089                    entry("fa2_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
090                    entry("fa3_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
091                    entry("fa4_unsorted_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
092                    entry("slbpa_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
093                    entry("dlcl_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
094                    entry("mlcl_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
095                    entry("lcb_pre_event", this::newLcb),
096                    entry("lcb_post_event", this::cleanLcb),
097                    entry("fa_pre_event", this::newFa),
098                    entry("fa_post_event", this::appendFa),
099                    entry("db_single_position_pre_event", this::setIsomericLevel),
100                    entry("db_single_position_post_event", this::addDbPosition),
101                    entry("db_position_number_pre_event", this::addDbPositionNumber),
102                    entry("cistrans_pre_event", this::addCistrans),
103                    entry("ether_pre_event", this::addEther),
104                    entry("old_hydroxyl_pre_event", this::addOldHydroxyl),
105                    entry("db_count_pre_event", this::addDoubleBonds),
106                    entry("carbon_pre_event", this::addCarbon),
107                    entry("hydroxyl_pre_event", this::addHydroxyl),
108                    entry("adduct_info_pre_event", this::newAdduct),
109                    entry("adduct_pre_event", this::addAdduct),
110                    entry("charge_pre_event", this::addCharge),
111                    entry("charge_sign_pre_event", this::addChargeSign),
112                    entry("lpl_pre_event", this::setMolecularSubspeciesLevel),
113                    entry("plasmalogen_pre_event", this::setPlasmalogen),
114                    entry("mediator_pre_event", this::setMediator),
115                    entry("mediator_post_event", this::addMediator),
116                    entry("unstructured_mediator_pre_event", this::setUnstructuredMediator),
117                    entry("trivial_mediator_pre_event", this::setTrivialMediator),
118                    entry("mediator_carbon_pre_event", this::setMediatorCarbon),
119                    entry("mediator_db_pre_event", this::setMediatorDB),
120                    entry("mediator_mono_functions_pre_event", this::setMediatorFunction),
121                    entry("mediator_di_functions_pre_event", this::setMediatorFunction),
122                    entry("mediator_position_pre_event", this::setMediatorFunctionPosition),
123                    entry("mediator_functional_group_post_event", this::addMediatorFunction),
124                    entry("mediator_suffix_pre_event", this::addMediatorSuffix),
125                    entry("mediator_tetranor_pre_event", this::setMediatorTetranor)
126            );
127
128        } catch (Exception e) {
129            throw new LipidParsingException("Cannot initialize GoslinParserEventHandler");
130        }
131    }

133    @Override
134    protected void resetParser(TreeNode node) {
135        content = null;
136        level = LipidLevel.FULL_STRUCTURE;
137        headGroup = "";
138        lcb = null;
139        faList.clear();
140        currentFa = null;
141        adduct = null;
142        dbPosition = 0;
143        dbCistrans = "";
144        plasmalogen = '\0';
145        mediatorFunction = "";
146        mediatorFunctionPositions.clear();
147        mediatorSuffix = false;
148        useHeadGroup = false;
149    }
150
151    private void setHeadGroupName(TreeNode node) {
152        headGroup = node.getText();
153    }
154
155    private void setSpeciesLevel(TreeNode node) {
156        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SPECIES);
157    }
158
159    private void setIsomericLevel(TreeNode node) {
160        dbPosition = 0;
161        dbCistrans = "";
162    }
163
164    private void addDbPosition(TreeNode node) {
165        if (currentFa != null) {
166            currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().put(dbPosition, dbCistrans);
167            if (!dbCistrans.equals("E") && !dbCistrans.equals("Z")) {
168                setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
169            }
170        }
171    }
172
173    private void setPlasmalogen(TreeNode node) {
174        plasmalogen = node.getText().toUpperCase().charAt(0);
175    }
176
177    private void addDbPositionNumber(TreeNode node) {
178        dbPosition = Integer.valueOf(node.getText());
179    }
180
181    private void addCistrans(TreeNode node) {
182        dbCistrans = node.getText();
183    }
184
185    private void setMolecularSubspeciesLevel(TreeNode node) {
186        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.MOLECULAR_SPECIES);
187    }
188
189    private void newFa(TreeNode node) {
190        LipidFaBondType lipid_FA_bond_type = LipidFaBondType.ESTER;
191        currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 2, null, null, lipid_FA_bond_type, knownFunctionalGroups);
192    }
193
194    private void newLcb(TreeNode node) {
195        lcb = new FattyAcid("LCB", knownFunctionalGroups);
196        lcb.setType(LipidFaBondType.LCB_REGULAR);
197        currentFa = lcb;
198        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
199    }
200
201    private void cleanLcb(TreeNode node) {
202        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().isEmpty() && currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() > 0) {
203            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SN_POSITION);
204        }
205        currentFa = null;
206    }
207
208    private void appendFa(TreeNode node) {
209        if (currentFa.getLipidFaBondType() == LipidFaBondType.ETHER_UNSPECIFIED) {
210            throw new LipidException("Lipid with unspecified ether bond cannot be treated properly.");
211        }
212        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getDoubleBondPositions().isEmpty() && currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() > 0) {
213            setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.SN_POSITION);
214        }
215
216        if (currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() < 0) {
217            throw new LipidException("Double bond count does not match with number of double bond positions");
218        }
219
220        faList.add(currentFa);
221        if (headGroup.compareTo("Sa") == 0 || headGroup.compareTo("So") == 0 || headGroup.compareTo("S1P") == 0 || headGroup.compareTo("Sa1P") == 0){
222            FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
223            if (headGroup.compareTo("Sa") == 0 || headGroup.compareTo("So") == 0){
224                functional_group.setCount(2);
225                currentFa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.LCB_EXCEPTION);
226            }
227            else {
228                functional_group.setCount(1);
229                currentFa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.LCB_REGULAR);
230            }
231            if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
232                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
233            }
234            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group);
235        }
236        currentFa = null;
237    }
238
239    private void buildLipid(TreeNode node) {
240        if (lcb != null) {
241            faList.add(0, lcb);
242            lcb = null;
243            currentFa = null;
244        }
245
246        if (plasmalogen != '\0' && faList.size() > 0 && lcb == null) {
247            faList.get(0).setLipidFaBondType(plasmalogen == 'O' ? LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMANYL : LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMENYL);
248        }
249
250        Headgroup headgroup = prepareHeadgroupAndChecks();
251
252        LipidAdduct lipid = new LipidAdduct(assembleLipid(headgroup), adduct);
253        content = lipid;
254
255    }
256
257    private void addEther(TreeNode node) {
258        String ether = node.getText();
259        if (ether.equals("a")) {
260            currentFa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMANYL);
261        } else if (ether.equals("p")) {
262            currentFa.setLipidFaBondType(LipidFaBondType.ETHER_PLASMENYL);
263            currentFa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(Math.max(0, currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() - 1));
264        }
265        plasmalogen = '\0';
266    }
267
268    private void addOldHydroxyl(TreeNode node) {
269        String old_hydroxyl = node.getText();
270        int num_h = 0;
271        if (old_hydroxyl.equals("d")) {
272            num_h = 2;
273        } else if (old_hydroxyl.equals("t")) {
274            num_h = 3;
275        }
276
277        if (spRegularLcb()) {
278            num_h -= 1;
279        }
280
281        FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
282        functional_group.setCount(num_h);
283        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
284            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
285        }
286        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group);
287    }
288
289    private void addDoubleBonds(TreeNode node) {
290        currentFa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(Integer.valueOf(node.getText()));
291    }
292
293    private void addCarbon(TreeNode node) {
294        currentFa.setNumCarbon(Integer.valueOf(node.getText()));
295    }
296
297    private void addHydroxyl(TreeNode node) {
298        int num_h = Integer.valueOf(node.getText());
299
300        if (spRegularLcb()) {
301            num_h -= 1;
302        }
303        if (num_h <= 0) return;
304
305        FunctionalGroup functional_group = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
306        functional_group.setCount(num_h);
307        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey("OH")) {
308            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
309        }
310        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functional_group);
311        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
312    }
313
314    private void newAdduct(TreeNode node) {
315        adduct = new Adduct("", "");
316    }
317
318    private void addAdduct(TreeNode node) {
319        adduct.setAdductString(node.getText());
320    }
321
322    private void addCharge(TreeNode node) {
323        adduct.setCharge(Integer.valueOf(node.getText()));
324    }
325
326    private void addChargeSign(TreeNode node) {
327        String sign = node.getText();
328        if (sign.equals("+")) {
329            adduct.setChargeSign(1);
330        } else if (sign.equals("-")) {
331            adduct.setChargeSign(-1);
332        }
333    }

335    private void setMediator(TreeNode node) {
336        headGroup = "FA";
337        currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", knownFunctionalGroups);
338        faList.add(currentFa);
339        setLipidLevel(LipidLevel.STRUCTURE_DEFINED);
340    }

342    private void setUnstructuredMediator(TreeNode node) {
343        headGroup = node.getText();

345        faList.clear();
346    }

348    private void setMediatorTetranor(TreeNode node) {
349        currentFa.setNumCarbon(currentFa.getNumCarbon() - 4);
350    }

352    private void setMediatorCarbon(TreeNode node) {
353        currentFa.setNumCarbon(currentFa.getNumCarbon() + MEDIATOR_FA.get(node.getText()));
354    }

358    }

360    private void setMediatorFunction(TreeNode node) {
361        mediatorFunction = node.getText();
362    }

364    private void setMediatorFunctionPosition(TreeNode node) {
365        mediatorFunctionPositions.add(node.getInt());
366    }
367
368    private void addMediatorFunction(TreeNode node) {
369        FunctionalGroup functionalGroup = null;
370        String fg = "";
371        if (mediatorFunction.equals("H")) {
372            functionalGroup = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
373            fg = "OH";
374            if (mediatorFunctionPositions.size() > 0) {
375                functionalGroup.setPosition(mediatorFunctionPositions.get(0));
376            }
377        } else if (mediatorFunction.equals("Oxo")) {
378            functionalGroup = knownFunctionalGroups.get("oxo");
379            fg = "oxo";
380            if (mediatorFunctionPositions.size() > 0) {
381                functionalGroup.setPosition(mediatorFunctionPositions.get(0));
382            }
383        } else if (mediatorFunction.equals("Hp")) {
384            functionalGroup = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OOH");
385            fg = "OOH";
386            if (mediatorFunctionPositions.size() > 0) {
387                functionalGroup.setPosition(mediatorFunctionPositions.get(0));
388            }
389        } else if (mediatorFunction.equals("E") || mediatorFunction.equals("Ep")) {
390            functionalGroup = knownFunctionalGroups.get("Ep");
391            fg = "Ep";
392            if (mediatorFunctionPositions.size() > 0) {
393                functionalGroup.setPosition(mediatorFunctionPositions.get(0));
394            }
395        } else if (mediatorFunction.equals("DH") || mediatorFunction.equals("DiH") || mediatorFunction.equals("diH")) {
396            functionalGroup = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
397            fg = "OH";
398            if (mediatorFunctionPositions.size() > 0) {
399                functionalGroup.setPosition(mediatorFunctionPositions.get(0));
400                FunctionalGroup functionalGroup2 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
401                functionalGroup2.setPosition(mediatorFunctionPositions.get(1));
402                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put("OH", new ArrayList<>());
403                currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get("OH").add(functionalGroup2);
404            }
405        }
406
407        if (!currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().containsKey(fg)) {
408            currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().put(fg, new ArrayList<>());
409        }
410        currentFa.getFunctionalGroupsInternal().get(fg).add(functionalGroup);
411    }

413    private void setTrivialMediator(TreeNode node) {
414        headGroup = "FA";
415
416        switch (node.getText()) {
417            case "Palmitic acid":
418                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 16, knownFunctionalGroups);
419                break;
420
421            case "Linoleic acid":
422                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 18, new DoubleBonds(2), knownFunctionalGroups);
423                break;
424
425            case "AA":
426                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 20, new DoubleBonds(4), knownFunctionalGroups);
427                break;
428
429            case "ALA":
430                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 18, new DoubleBonds(3), knownFunctionalGroups);
431                break;
432
433            case "EPA":
434                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 20, new DoubleBonds(5), knownFunctionalGroups);
435                break;
436
437            case "DHA":
438                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 22, new DoubleBonds(6), knownFunctionalGroups);
439                break;
440
441            case "LTB4": {
442                FunctionalGroup f1 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
443                FunctionalGroup f2 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
444                f1.setPosition(5);
445                f2.setPosition(12);
446                DoubleBonds db = new DoubleBonds(new TreeMap<>(Map.of(6, "Z", 8, "E", 10, "E", 14, "Z")));
447                HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fg = new HashMap<>(Map.of("OH", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f1, f2))));
448                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 20, db, fg, knownFunctionalGroups);
449            }
450            break;
451
452            case "Resolvin D3": {
453                FunctionalGroup f1 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
454                FunctionalGroup f2 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
455                FunctionalGroup f3 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
456                f1.setPosition(4);
457                f2.setPosition(11);
458                f3.setPosition(17);
459                HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fg = new HashMap<>(Map.of("OH", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f1, f2, f3))));
460                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 22, new DoubleBonds(6), fg, knownFunctionalGroups);
461            }
462            break;
463
464            case "Maresin 1": {
465                FunctionalGroup f1 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
466                FunctionalGroup f2 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
467                f1.setPosition(4);
468                f2.setPosition(14);
469                HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fg = new HashMap<>(Map.of("OH", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f1, f2))));
470                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 22, new DoubleBonds(6), fg, knownFunctionalGroups);
471            }
472            break;
473
474            case "Resolvin D2": {
475                FunctionalGroup f1 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
476                FunctionalGroup f2 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
477                FunctionalGroup f3 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
478                f1.setPosition(4);
479                f2.setPosition(16);
480                f3.setPosition(17);
481                HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fg = new HashMap<>(Map.of("OH", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f1, f2, f3))));
482                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 22, new DoubleBonds(6), fg, knownFunctionalGroups);
483            }
484            break;
485
486            case "Resolvin D5": {
487                FunctionalGroup f1 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
488                FunctionalGroup f2 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
489                f1.setPosition(7);
490                f2.setPosition(17);
491                HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fg = new HashMap<>(Map.of("OH", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f1, f2))));
492                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 22, new DoubleBonds(6), fg, knownFunctionalGroups);
493            }
494            break;
495
496            case "Resolvin D1": {
497                FunctionalGroup f1 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
498                FunctionalGroup f2 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
499                FunctionalGroup f3 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
500                f1.setPosition(7);
501                f2.setPosition(8);
502                f3.setPosition(17);
503                HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fg = new HashMap<>(Map.of("OH", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f1, f2, f3))));
504                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 22, new DoubleBonds(6), fg, knownFunctionalGroups);
505            }
506            break;
507
508            case "TXB1": {
509                FunctionalGroup f1 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
510                FunctionalGroup f2 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
511                FunctionalGroup f3 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
512                FunctionalGroup f4 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("oxy");
513                f1.setPosition(15);
514                f2.setPosition(9);
515                f3.setPosition(11);
516                f4.setPosition(11);
517                HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fgc = new HashMap<>(Map.of("OH", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f2, f3)), "oxo", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f4))));
518                Cycle cy = new Cycle(5, 8, 12, fgc, knownFunctionalGroups);
519                HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fg = new HashMap<>(Map.of("OH", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f1)), "cy", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(cy))));
520                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 20, new DoubleBonds(1), fg, knownFunctionalGroups);
521            }
522            break;
523
524            case "TXB2": {
525                FunctionalGroup f1 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
526                FunctionalGroup f2 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
527                FunctionalGroup f3 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
528                FunctionalGroup f4 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("oxy");
529                f1.setPosition(15);

531                f3.setPosition(11);
532                f4.setPosition(11);
533                HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fgc = new HashMap<>(Map.of("OH", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f2, f3)), "oxy", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f4))));
534                Cycle cy = new Cycle(5, 8, 12, fgc, knownFunctionalGroups);
535                HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fg = new HashMap<>(Map.of("OH", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f1)), "cy", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(cy))));
536                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 20, new DoubleBonds(2), fg, knownFunctionalGroups);
537            }
538            break;
539
540            case "TXB3": {
541                FunctionalGroup f1 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
542                FunctionalGroup f2 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
543                FunctionalGroup f3 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("OH");
544                FunctionalGroup f4 = knownFunctionalGroups.get("oxy");
545                f1.setPosition(15);
546                f2.setPosition(9);
547                f3.setPosition(11);
548                f4.setPosition(11);
549                HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fgc = new HashMap<>(Map.of("OH", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f2, f3)), "oxy", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f4))));
550                Cycle cy = new Cycle(5, 8, 12, fgc, knownFunctionalGroups);
551                HashMap<String, ArrayList<FunctionalGroup>> fg = new HashMap<>(Map.of("OH", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(f1)), "cy", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(cy))));
552                currentFa = new FattyAcid("FA", 20, new DoubleBonds(3), fg, knownFunctionalGroups);
553            }

628    private void addMediatorSuffix(TreeNode node) {
629        mediatorSuffix = true;
630    }
631
632    private void addMediator(TreeNode node) {
633        if (!mediatorSuffix) {
634            currentFa.getDoubleBonds().setNumDoubleBonds(currentFa.getDoubleBonds().getNumDoubleBonds() - 1);
635        }
